    {
      "text": "America's favorite family card game is mixed with the modern poker craze to create Uno 52. Ten themed backgrounds set the stage in this fast-paced game from America’s favorite toymaker. Four styles of Poker play, including Solitaire and Challenge means the fun never stops!",
